search_results.title: Kish Kash
search_results.snippet: Kish Kash is the third studio album by English electronic music duo Basement Jaxx, released on 20 October 2003 by XL Recordings and Astralwerks.

search_results.title: Kish Kash: Authentic Couscous in NYC
search_results.snippet: Kish Kash may be the first NYC cafe focused on couscous and tagines. Kosher meat and no dairy make this great news for all eaters.
